= Installing and Editing ODL Documentation =
<ol>
<li> Change to the sdndocs-maven-plugin directory and use the '''mvn install''' command to install the toolchain.</li>
<li> Change to the odl-documentation directory and use the  '''mvn install''' command to install the documentation. </li>
<li> Access the guides at ''odl-documentation/manuals/install-guide/target/docbkx/webhelp/user-guide'' </li>
</ol>

